        <Parent_String>excrement [300191590], animal material by excretions, secretions, and fluids [300191589], animal material by form or function [300191588], animal material [300011793], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
